long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
# Play more games on the top-left menu.

Getaway Shooter is a chaotic two-player racing game where you compete against three others to reach the extraction point. Your only means of movement is by jumping left or right, making navigation in this game quite challenging! Grab guns and various weapons along the way to fend off your opponents!

How to Play

Play solo or with a friend
Team up with a friend using the same keyboard or dive into the single-player mode. Choose one of the characters and join the game!
Jump to Move

Once the race begins, you can only move by jumping left or right. This movement style creates a chaotic scene! The distance you cover depends on the timing of your jumps in either direction.
Anything Can Happen

There are multiple rounds in the race, each taking place in a different location. Race to the finish line, pick up weapons, and encounter various upgrades along the way. Utilize weapons to attack other racers on the path to victory!
Features

Challenging "jump to move" mechanic
Weapons and power-ups
Multiple racing locations
Explore a variety of unlockable characters
